00:32:49,218 --> 00:32:50,636
Kami baik-baik saja.

356
00:32:51,887 --> 00:32:52,805
Kenapa?

357
00:32:53,555 --> 00:32:54,515
Entahlah.

358
00:32:55,349 --> 00:32:57,226
