00:33:21,416 --> 00:33:22,543
Apa maksudmu?

366
00:33:23,836 --> 00:33:24,962
Aku hanya mengingatkan.

367
00:33:27,089 --> 00:33:29,633
Ikuti apa yang kau yakini,
