00:36:14,423 --> 00:36:15,716
Kau suka berkunjung?

409
00:36:19,052 --> 00:36:20,053
Bergantung padamu.

410
00:36:21,596 --> 00:36:23,015
Kau cepat belajar, ya.

411
00:36:28,228 --> 00:36:30,063
Aku mau menemuimu setiap hari.

412
00:36:31,732 --> 00:36:34,109
Kau tak tahu seberapa inginnya aku

413
00:36:34,693 --> 00:36:36,570
