414
00:36:38,488 --> 00:36:39,531
Namun?

415
00:36:41,491 --> 00:36:43,744
Kalau aku memaksakan diri
dan kehilangan dirimu?

416
00:36:44,953 --> 00:36:46,288
Kau takkan datang dua kali.

417
00:36:50,125 --> 00:36:52,085
