433
00:38:33,812 --> 00:38:35,856
Mataku kelilipan.

434
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:37,482
Yang benar saja.

435
00:38:39,943 --> 00:38:41,486
Kau menangis.

436
00:38:43,905 --> 00:38:45,115
Sampai besok.

437
00:38:45,615 --> 00:38:48,535
Lembur selama ini
harus diganjar minum-minum.

438
00:38:48,869 --> 00:38:50,829
Tentu saja. Kau mau ikut?

439
00:38:56,918 --> 00:38:59,254
Tentu. Aku yang traktir.

440
00:39:00,755 --> 00:39:01,756
Tentu.

