458
00:40:07,739 --> 00:40:08,573
Baik.

459
00:40:08,657 --> 00:40:11,701
Ini tak mengubah apa pun.

460
00:40:13,662 --> 00:40:14,955
Ji-ho juga begitu.

461
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:20,460
