462
00:40:22,462 --> 00:40:24,297
tapi jika aku begitu penting bagimu,

463
00:40:25,924 --> 00:40:27,926
kau akan tahu harus apa
untuk tetap hormat.

464
00:40:30,178 --> 00:40:32,389
Kau pasti paham, 'kan?

465
00:40:33,265 --> 00:40:34,307
Ya.

466
00:40:39,813 --> 00:40:40,855
Mari saling hormat.

467
00:40:41,606 --> 00:40:42,566
Tentu saja.

468
00:40:54,160 --> 00:40:56,121
Bagaimana proses pindahannya?

469
00:40:57,956 --> 00:40:59,708
Sedang berlangsung.

470
00:41:00,458 --> 00:41:01,418
Syukurlah.

471
00:41:02,377 --> 00:41:05,755
